name: Flock
description: Bringing real world farming to the Blockchain. It's simple , We have sheep and every time they give birth as a reward we airdrop more tokens to holders every 6 months from the airdrop reward pool. Our flock is growing daily and currently we have 350 female sheep waiting to give birth.... Dog's and Turtle's have dominated this space for too long. Time to let the sheep shine... Let's grow the flock together! Real sheep... Real Utility.... Real Rewards...!
